data.name: ReadCsePersonAccount
data.value: select top(1) CSP_NUMBER, TYPE from CKT_CSE_PERSON_ACC where (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (TYPE = 'R')

data.name: ReadStmtCouponSuppStatusHist
data.value: select CPA_TYPE, CSP_NUMBER, COLL_ID, TYPE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, DOC_TYPE_TO_SUPP from CKT_STMT_SUP_ST_HS where (@cpaType = CPA_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (TYPE = 'R') order by EFFECTIVE_DATE desc
